
⸻

FG-451 — Merits OA “Ten-Line Script”
	•	⚖️ Core Message: Memorize a 10-line cadence: QP → Std → 2 pins → Relief ladder → Scope → Close.
	•	📖 Lesson Content: Write in numbered lines; rehearse to 75 seconds; repeat cadence in rebuttal.
	•	📝 Assignment: Draft your 10-line OA script today.
	•	✅ Model Response: “1. QP. 2. Standard. 3–4. Two pins. 5–7. Relief ladder. 8. Scope guard. 9–10. Close (remand 21d).”
	•	💡 Reflection Summary: Rhythm beats improvisation.
	•	🎨 Visual Concept: Ten numbered bars, last two glowing red.

⸻

FG-452 — Merits Findings Gap Table
	•	⚖️ Core Message: Visualize skipped findings with a table.
	•	📖 Lesson Content: Rows: Factor • Raised (pin) • Skipped (line) • Relief. Keep ≤1 page.
	•	📝 Assignment: Draft a 4-row findings gap table.
	•	✅ Model Response: “Harm — raised Dkt 14:3 — skipped Dkt 18:2 — Relief: remand 21d.”
	•	💡 Reflection Summary: Gaps persuade.
	•	🎨 Visual Concept: A 4-row table with one greyed cell.

