FG-453 — Merits Amicus Ladder
	•	⚖️ Core Message: Amici should adopt your relief ladder explicitly.
	•	📖 Lesson Content: Coordination note: “Amicus adopts grant/vacate/remand/clarify ladder, scope limited to ¶3.” Post to bank.
	•	📝 Assignment: Draft a 6-line amicus adoption note.
	•	✅ Model Response: “Amicus A adopts relief ladder. Scope limited. Mirrors posted; SHA-256 ….”
	•	💡 Reflection Summary: Harmony multiplies effect.
	•	🎨 Visual Concept: Two amicus tiles feeding one relief ladder.

