FG-454 — Merits Release Table
	•	⚖️ Core Message: Post a table logging every merits doc with hash.
	•	📖 Lesson Content: Columns: Date • Doc • SHA-256 • Mirrors • Next step. Post to microsite.
	•	📝 Assignment: Draft a 5-row release table for merits.
	•	✅ Model Response: “09/01 — Opening brief — sha … — Mirrors M-1/M-2 — Reply due 09/15.”
	•	💡 Reflection Summary: Transparency builds trust.
	•	🎨 Visual Concept: A table with fingerprint column.

