FG-455 — Merits Reply “Raised/Skipped” Sidebar
	•	⚖️ Core Message: Replies should highlight omissions visually.
	•	📖 Lesson Content: Sidebar: Issue • Raised (pin) • Skipped (line); neutral phrasing; end with relief line.
	•	📝 Assignment: Draft a 3-row sidebar for your reply.
	•	✅ Model Response: “Equities — Dkt 14:5 — Skipped Dkt 18:2 — Relief: remand 21d.”
	•	💡 Reflection Summary: Visuals guide clerks.
	•	🎨 Visual Concept: Sidebar with red “Skipped” cells.

