	•	📝 Assignment: Draft your appendix legend today.
	•	✅ Model Response: “Cites are to PDF pages. Ex = exhibit page. Appx = Tab page. SHA-256 ….”
	•	💡 Reflection Summary: Legends save hours.
	•	🎨 Visual Concept: A one-page legend with fingerprint footer.

