FG-458 — Merits Relief Card Trio
	•	⚖️ Core Message: Carry three cards: Grant, Remand, Clarify.
	•	📖 Lesson Content: Card 1 = Grant (wrong test). Card 2 = Remand (21d). Card 3 = Clarify (n.3). Hash all three.
	•	📝 Assignment: Draft your trio and hash them.
	•	✅ Model Response: “Card 1—Grant. Card 2—Remand 21d. Card 3—Clarify n.3.”
	•	💡 Reflection Summary: Small cards, strong memory.
	•	🎨 Visual Concept: Three palm cards with hash tags.

