FG-459 — Merits OA Backup Plan
	•	⚖️ Core Message: Redundancy prevents disaster.
	•	📖 Lesson Content: Two devices logged; dial-in saved; packet local; file contingency notice with alt windows.
	•	📝 Assignment: Draft your OA backup checklist.
	•	✅ Model Response: “Primary Zoom; backup phone; packet local; alt window Tue/Wed 2–4 PM.”
	•	💡 Reflection Summary: Redundancy = resilience.
	•	🎨 Visual Concept: Laptop + phone icons with a clock.

