FG-460 — Merits Closeout Bundle
	•	⚖️ Core Message: Archive merits phase cleanly.
	•	📖 Lesson Content: Bundle: Brief.pdf; Reply.pdf; Appendix.pdf; OA cards; CHECKSUMS.txt; ReleaseNote.md. Post mirrors; hash.
	•	📝 Assignment: Build closeout ZIP + 100-word note.
	•	✅ Model Response: “Release v6—Merits closeout kit posted; Brief (sha …), Reply (sha …), Appendix (sha …). Mirrors aligned.”
	•	💡 Reflection Summary: Closure is public memory.
	•	🎨 Visual Concept: A ribboned ZIP with doc tiles and a fingerprint